buyerAgent.name: Lisa Kay Meyer - Kittle Real Estate

data.description:
Home is back on the market at no fault to sellers! Sellers are offering a $10,000 seller concession. Come out and see it!

Beautiful home for an amazing price! Primary room is on the upper floor near family room while two additional bedrooms are tucked quietly on the lower level. Eat in kitchen has a lot of cabinet space and beautiful appliances included! Back yard is like an oasis with a beautiful covered back deck, spacious yard, play set, garden beds, shed, and green house. Hot tub included!
